                    "paymentTerms": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>For customization&nbsp;packages without Flights:<span style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></strong></span></p>\n<table class=\"terms_table_pdp_data table-responsive\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 157px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 25px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 279px; height: 25px;\"><strong>Payment Procedure Minimum Per Person Payment to be made by the client*</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 139px; height: 25px;\"><strong>Charges</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 7px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 279px; height: 7px;\">At the time of booking</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 139px; height: 7px;\">\n<p>INR 15,000/- per person</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 279px; height: 33px;\">Within 31 - 45 days prior to the date of departure</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 139px; height: 33px;\">75% of the holiday cost</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 279px; height: 33px;\">Less than 30 &amp; below from the date of departure</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 139px; height: 33px;\">100% of the holiday cost</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><u><span style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></u><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>For customization&nbsp;packages inclusive of Flights:<span style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></strong></span></p>\n<table class=\"terms_table_pdp_data table-responsive\" style=\"width: 421px; height: 158px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 34px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 222.674px; height: 34px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Payment Procedure Minimum Per Person Payment to be made by the client*</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 189.326px; height: 34px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Charges</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 222.674px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">At the time of booking</td>\n<td style=\"width: 189.326px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">Full Payments towards Air Tickets +&nbsp;Defined Minimum Booking Deposit / 10% Payment Towards Land Package</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 222.674px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">Within 31 - 45 days prior to the date of departure</td>\n<td style=\"width: 189.326px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">75% of the holiday cost</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 32px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 222.674px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">Less than 30 &amp; below from the date of departure</td>\n<td style=\"width: 189.326px; height: 32px; text-align: center;\">100% of the holiday cost</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><strong>Notes:<br /><br /></strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">*For Non-refundable &amp; time-limit itineraries 100% payment is required to confirm a booking.&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">All payments towards the tour cost must be made by the client to the company in accordance with the procedure and time frame mentioned herein below&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">*For Air tickets being issued / blocked on time limit: Full INR component will be collected before issuance, else price will be subject to change.&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">*Initial Booking deposit will be collected as per the amount mentioned or the Package Price whichever is lower&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Full payment must be made in accordance with the procedure stated above. In case of non-compliance thereto by the client, the company reserves a right to cancel the tour/booking of the client with subsequent loss of deposit and apply and recover the cancellation charges as mentioned herein</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">To obtain hotel confirmation letter / visa letter for visa application purpose, minimum 50% of the total package price needs to be paid.</li>\n</ol>",
